---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Maps & Routes" description="Bike maps, routes, and cycling infrastructure resources for Los Angeles.">
  <p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-6">
    Explore cycling routes and infrastructure across Los Angeles.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">LA City Bike Map</h2>
  <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
    The City of Los Angeles maintains an official bike map showing bike lanes, paths, and routes throughout the city.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">Metro Bike Share</h2>
  <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
    Metro Bike Share provides short-term bicycle rentals at stations across Los Angeles, with options for single rides, daily passes, and monthly memberships.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">Popular Routes</h2>
  <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
    Coming soon — a curated list of popular cycling routes in the LA area.
  </p>
</PageLayout>
